metadata.name: Swirls | Loie Hollowell  #2
metadata.description: Swirls are found throughout the universe and in nature. They can be energetic , exciting, hypnotic, and mysterious. This is a limited collection of 5000 spirals by Loie Hollowell. Hollowell has been creating generative art since the 1980s. He is an artist, software developer and father of 2.
